{"tid":1697994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(連燈)  《花木蘭》劉亦菲入選2019荷里活新星","createTime":"2019-11-07T08:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T08:14:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a2b0a5bfd7478833d228b71a1759e54462d667","tid":1697994,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"《好萊塢報導》（The Hollywood Reporter）近日公布了「2019好萊塢新星」名單，其中華人圈唯一入榜的女演員就是飾演迪士尼真人版《花木蘭》的女星─劉亦菲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/11/07/99/7036781.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F11%2F07%2F99%2F7036781.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=ac3cf0d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／擷自hollywoodreporter<br />\n<br />\n電影《花木蘭》從預告發布後就因「過度改編」引發了不小的負評，到女主角劉亦菲在社群上轉發「我支持香港警察，你們可以打我了 What a shame for Hong Kong」的圖文引來許多歐美網友揚言抵制，最近又傳出該片將大規模重拍，這部電影的產出過程可以說是問題不斷、困難重重。<br />\n<br />\n雖然發生了這麼多不順的事情，但是劉亦菲仍然入選了2019好萊塢新星的名單，這也足見了她現在在電影圈有著一定程度的影響力。除了是華人圈唯一入榜的女演員外，她亦是名單中年紀最長的明星，而名單中年紀最小的則是今年18歲的伊莎貝拉莫娜（Isabela Merced）。<br />\n<br />\n而在報導中，劉亦菲表示她最想與導演戴倫艾洛諾夫斯基（Darren Aronofsky）合作、早上起床第一個打開的App是通訊軟體微信、去KTV會唱冰雪奇緣的主題曲〈Let It Go〉，而最欣賞的明星是娜塔莉波曼（Natalie Portman）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://style.udn.com/style/story/8065/4149728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstyle.udn.com%2Fstyle%2Fstory%2F8065%2F4149728&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=adcc6d4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://style.udn.com/style/story/8065/4149728</a>"},{"pid":"75195ba5aa667e821a13918f99ed42c965540d27","tid":1697994,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:14:15.000Z","msg":"Isabela Merced<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}